<h1>Rebelião camponesa em Caquetá escancara o problema agrário e nacional da Colômbia - A Nova Democracia</h1>
<p>Author: Ângelo de Carvalho</p>
<p>Description: Exaustos da negligência da empresa, os camponeses e indígenas cercaram um dos campos de extração de petróleo da multinacional imperialista e atearam fogo nas</p>
<p>Publish Time: 2023-03-13T14:38:58-03:00</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-03-13T14:39:19-03:00</p>
<p>Updated Time: 2023-03-13T14:39:19-03:00</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://anovademocracia.com.br/storage/2023/03/Working-day-with-machinery-in-the-banana-plantations-in-Magdalena-Source-Photography-th.png">Working-day-with-machinery-in-the-banana-plantations-in-Magdalena-Source-Photography-th.png</a>']</p>
